<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lastly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lastly,</orth> 1) in the last place: <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.142" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 142</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.221" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 1, 221</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 9, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.54" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.6.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 6, 27</bibl>.<lb />2) in the conclusion, finally, to boot: <cit><quote>l. hurried here to this place,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 105</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>l. myself unkindly banished,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 3, 104</bibl></cit>.
